Acceleor Profils Links Extension:
Tool to improve productivity of agents by helping them converting profiles links types.
The tool is using a list of profils links, and converts them into another type of links.
A table output with intermediate results is also available for download.
The format of the table is user friendly, and can be downloaded for off-line consultation.
This tool was created as a collaboration between ACCELEOR and PRF Development.
